    "synopsis": "On the oceanic world of Pelago — a backwater of fisherfolk who barely know there is an Imperium — old Tidon recounts to his young apprentice the strangest catch of his life. As a young man he sailed with his mentor Ven and his cousin Sareo when a stolen Alpha Legion stormbird came screaming out of the sky and crashed into the swell beside their boat. Boarding the half-sunken hulk, they found a single survivor still alive in the wreckage: a Space Wolf named Felbjorn, one of the Vlka Fenryka watchers Leman Russ had placed aboard his brother Alpharius's ships. What he had seen would not stay on his world.",
